==Chinese==
===Pronunciation===
====[[wikipedia:Standard_Mandarin|Mandarin]]====
[[Pinyin]]: '''rù xiāng suí sú'''

====[[wikipedia:Min Nan|Min Nan]]====
[[wikipedia:POJ|POJ]]: <font face="Lucida Sans Unicode">li̍p-hiong-sûi-sio̍k</font>

===Etymology===
Literally: When entering a village, follow the customs.

===Proverb===
'''[[入]][[鄉]][[隨]][[俗]]'''

# [[when in Rome, do as the Romans do]].

===Alternate forms===
[[入乡随俗]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

===Related terms===
*[[入]][[境]][[隨]][[俗]]

